PrecisAuthority to enter into a FINAL SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT with the CANOE LAKE CREE NATION to resolve a claim respecting its loss of access to unoccupied Crown lands which precluded them from continuing their traditional occupations of fishing, hunting and trapping, as guaranteed by Treaty No. 10, due to the creation of the Primrose Lake Air Weapons Range.

precis:
Authority to enter into a FINAL SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT with the CANOE LAKE
CREE NATION to resolve a claim respecting its loss of access to unoccupied
Crown lands which precluded them from continuing their traditional
occupations of fishing, hunting and trapping, as guaranteed by Treaty
No. 10, due to the creation of the Primrose Lake Air Weapons Range.
